@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
@ftpConfigSeq = 1

### ──────────────────────────────────────
### FTP 설정 관리
### ──────────────────────────────────────

### 1. FTP 설정 목록 조회 → 200
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ftp-configs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. 토큰 없이 조회 → 401
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ftp-configs

### 3. FTP 설정 등록 (글로벌 기본) → 201
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ftp-configs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ftpName": "기본 FTP 서버",
  "ftpHost": "ftp.konkuk.ac.kr",
  "ftpPort": 21,
  "ftpUsername": "recorder_user",
  "ftpPassword": "ftp_password",
  "ftpPath": "/recordings/",
  "ftpProtocol": "FTP",
  "ftpPassiveMode": "Y",
  "isDefault": "Y"
}

### 4. FTP 설정 등록 (녹화기 전용) → 201
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ftp-configs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ftpName": "101호 전용 SFTP",
  "ftpHost": "10.0.1.100",
  "ftpPort": 22,
  "ftpUsername": "sftp_user",
  "ftpPassword": "sftp_password",
  "ftpPath": "/101/",
  "ftpProtocol": "SFTP",
  "ftpPassiveMode": "N",
  "isDefault": "N",
  "recorderSeq": 1
}

### 5. FTP 설정 수정 → 200
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ftp-configs/{{ftpConfigSeq}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ftpName": "기본 FTP 서버 (변경)",
  "ftpHost": "ftp2.konkuk.ac.kr",
  "ftpPort": 2121,
  "ftpPath": "/new-recordings/"
}

### 6. FTP 설정 수정 (비밀번호 변경) → 200
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ftp-configs/{{ftpConfigSeq}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ftpPassword": "new_password_123"
}

### 7. FTP 설정 삭제 → 200
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ftp-configs/{{ftpConfigSeq}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. FTP 설정 삭제 (존재하지 않는 ID) → 404
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ftp-configs/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. FTP 연결 테스트 → 200
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ftp-configs/{{ftpConfigSeq}}/test
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. FTP 연결 테스트 (존재하지 않는 ID) → 404
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ftp-configs/99999/test
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
